title: Do We believe Tekashi69 ??
itunes:title: Do We believe Tekashi69 ??
description:
Monday 7/23- Today on the show after news hit about Tekashi69 getting pistol whipped and robbed we opened up the phone lines to see if our listeners believed this story about him, since he is well known for clout chasing. Moreover, we opened up the phone lines to see if any of our listeners expect money back after lending it, once video surfaced of Tiffany Haddish trying to give back money to Kevin Hart he lend to her years ago. Also, Charlamagne, gave "Donkey of the Day" to a man that called in a bomb threat so he would not miss his flight.
